      "text": "Building Utopia is a social simulation in a sense that it simulates some of the processes of society as a complex system. So more precisely it is a representation of society as a symbolic system. Contrary to the Social Simulation as an academic field - Building Utopia is interdisciplinary and borrows elements of [[Systems Modelling]], Social Simulation, and uses [[Performance]] to replace [[Agent Based Simulation]]."
